style.css:
:root {
  --roundness: 50px; /* edit roundness of icons from 0px to 50px */
 --main-color: #007dbd; /* Main Color */     
  --hover-color: #03679b; /* Hover Color */
  --home-color: #eee; /* Change home icon color */
  --home-size: 24px; /* size of the home icon */
  --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,.4); /* change to darken lighten, or set to transparent */
 --background-image: url(https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/60/c4/bb/60c4bb55215c989b15b0fe144c73cf82.jpg); /* change background */
  --background-blur: 0px; /* Main Background Blur */
--popup-background: url(https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/60/c4/bb/60c4bb55215c989b15b0fe144c73cf82.jpg);  /* Background for popups and modals */
  --background-darkness: 0.75; /* change the darkness of your background. 1 makes it completely black, 0 makes it like the original image */
}
